import React from 'react'; import './Outcome.css'; const Outcome = () => { return (
{/* Desktop */}

Outcome

The redesign of the personal account dashboard led to measurable improvements in user experience and business outcomes:

Reduced CS inquiries

New features like payment management led to a 30% drop in customer support requests.

Increased user engagement

Users spent 20% more time in their accounts, finding it easier to access information.

Boost Upsell and Partner Offer Conversions

The introduction of exclusive deals and upsell opportunities boosted conversion rates by 15%.

Decreased time to complete key tasks

Users can now complete key actions like tracking orders and managing payments 25% faster.
